WEBVTT

00:00.005 --> 00:01.848
Robert is known as Mr. Sunny.

00:02.245 --> 00:04.686
He is over six feet, five inches tall,...

00:04.945 --> 00:07.259
...looking like a giant next to most people.

00:07.551 --> 00:11.793
He is from a bilingual background and speaks three languages fluently.

00:12.546 --> 00:13.906
This is Mary.

00:15.609 --> 00:17.223
She is a good person.

00:18.186 --> 00:20.167
She is nice to everybody.

00:21.868 --> 00:23.329
This is Luke.

00:24.766 --> 00:26.628
Our moms are friends.

00:28.272 --> 00:30.584
We like to play basketball together.

00:31.944 --> 00:34.604
Lastly, this is Jamie.

00:36.035 --> 00:37.793
She's my best friend.

00:39.083 --> 00:40.974
We do everything together.

